%% Vitruvian — Authentication Flow
%% How requests are authenticated via middleware and Supabase Auth

sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant MW as Middleware
    participant SA as Supabase Auth
    participant App as App Route

    B->>MW: HTTP Request
    MW->>SA: getUser() (validate session cookie)

    alt No valid session
        SA-->>MW: null user
        MW-->>B: 302 Redirect to /login
    else Valid session + auth route
        SA-->>MW: user object
        MW-->>B: 302 Redirect to /
    else Valid session + app route
        SA-->>MW: user object
        MW->>App: Forward request (cookies refreshed)
        App-->>B: HTML Response
    end
